Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}You may have been worried about me, but with the new year, I've got my old body back,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}so from now on, I, high school detective Shin'ichi Kudō, will solve any case in a flash—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm Shin'ichi Kudō, a high school detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}While at an amusement park with my childhood friend and classmate, Ra—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:42.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kaitō Kid realised that his disguise as Shin'ichi Kudō had been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:47.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How will he manage to escape?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:51.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or will he vanish with the dew on her fist?!
