Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:01:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Thanks to all of you, the TV show and the movie were very popular last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It was a packed year, as we even had a collaboration movie together with that thieving old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.73,0:01:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And as for the year to come...
Comment: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:22.43,Signs,detective,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's the 20th anniversary of the manga serialisation! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}All of us involved with the series will be giving all we can more than ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So please keep watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:55.90,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,0)}{＜影の黒さと闇の濃さ\N切り裂いてくのが推理の光＞\N}Only the light of deductions can tear apart black shadows and deep darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:59.64,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Kid's after a crimson diamond.\NTime to unveil his illustrious trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.24,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{＜たった１つの真実　見抜く\N}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.94,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{見た目は子供　頭脳は大人＞\N}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.24,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,250)}{＜その名は　名探偵コナン！＞\N}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:39.81,Narr,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,0)}Advisor Jirokichi Suzuki sponsored a special trip for the Bell Tree Express, hoping to capture Kaitō Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:45.84,Narr,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But the men in black took over the train in their attempts to erase Sherry — a.k.a. Ai Haibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:54.61,Narr,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And even Kaitō Kid, who was on the train to inspect it, ended up caught in the explosion when a carriage blew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What's the meaning of this, Superintendent Chaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}After the explosion on the Bell Tree Express the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}the jewel exhibition was supposed to be delayed until we'd closed the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Advisor Jirokichi Suzuki was pretty hard-set on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:17.68,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,{\blur1}He probably thought that since he'd got his hands on a gem that was likely to lure Kaitō Kid in, it'd be a shame not to show it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Anyway, for us police, it means we get another shot at catching Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But still, if that explosion was caused by some criminal targeting the jewel exhibition,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}then it'll get targeted again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We still don't know the truth behind that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I doubt Kid would stick his hands in something that dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Actually, a letter from Kid has already been delivered to the advisor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}saying he'll come to collect the gem on the first day of the exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:05:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Along with a message for the police, asking us to make sure that the exhibition hall doesn't get blown up this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And it looks like that gem can only be exhibited for a limited amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}A limited amount of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's not as though that billionaire's {\i1}renting{\i0} the gem...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Come to think of it, we haven't seen the jewel in question yet, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}No, we haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I hear it's going to be displayed in a large glass case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}According to the advisor, the jewel can move around freely in all directions in the glass case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}M-Move around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:48.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,Great Suzuki Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,16,,{\blur1}So let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I present before you a single can of cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}As you can see, it's been crushed, and there's nothing left inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:06:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And with the power of my will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I-It went back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And once I run my finger across the can, the stay-on-tab reverts to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And the cola inside remains intact!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Amazing, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}How did you do it? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}No can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Kid-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s coming tonight, and I want to perform it in front of him to surprise him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I don't think he'll be surprised at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Because look, there's a black sticker stuck to your thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Plus, that can has traces of two small holes in the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sonoko-{\i1}neechan{\i0} probably poured out half of the cola through the holes she'd made with a drill or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and then crushed the can and blocked the holes with glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then she stuck the black sticker at the mouth of the can to make it look like the can was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I get it! If you shake the can to prove there's nothing left inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}the cola would foam up and release carbon dioxide gas,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}which would smooth out all the dents in the can with the increase in pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then if you trace around the mouth of the can with your fingers and remove the sticker,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}it'll look as if the can had been miraculously mended, right, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That trick was on TV the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ran! Why'd you bring that annoying little brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Your uncle Jirokichi invited him, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Because Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s the 'Kid Killer'!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}More than that, I'm surprised you came, Sera-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I didn't think you'd be interested in stuff like phantom thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm certainly not {\i1}un{\i0}interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Holmes had Prof. Moriarty, Kogorō Akechi had the Fiend with Twenty Faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:08:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's natural for a detective to have a mysterious rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And anyway, I wanted to ask you about this hat that you picked up on the Bell Tree Express.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I just picked it up from the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then you didn't see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}A man wearing black clothes, a black hat, and had a burn all the way down his right cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So you came, Shirō's wee lass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I must apologise for the fiasco on the Bell Tree Express the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Wow, it's getting very crowded in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's expected, with Kid-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s popularity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Since we're here, why don't we look around the other exhibitions?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Wow! There are lots of people around that glass case!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}...an aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, hey, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's right. The object Kid wants this time is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The red diamond on this turtle's back — the Blush Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's stuck to the turtle's back, gold necklace chain and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There are a lot of jewels stuck on its belly, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You wanted to display this 10 centimetre long decorated turtle in the Bell Tree Express's first-class carriage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The aquarium's made from toughened glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The back is a concrete wall that's two metres thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:52.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The top and sides are a metal mesh made from a special alloy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and on top of that, his prey swims freely in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:10:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So even the so-called 'Moonlight Magician' shouldn't be able to steal this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Seems to be in pretty bad taste to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:08.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The animal protection league's probably gonna come down on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Actually, there's a story behind this turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I trust you've heard about the great Italian actress who died in an accident half a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's said that this is the turtle she kept as a pet, named 'Poseidon'!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Poseidon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The owner of the Blush Mermaid was her, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:33.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But why would she put the jewel on her pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The story goes that she desperately stuck the jewels onto the turtle with glue before the ship sank,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}hoping that the turtle would be saved and taken in by somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The jewels were both for breeding expenses and as a sign of her gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The local fishermen found it floating in the water along with the tank,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and by happy chance, it found its way into my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But have you actually had the jewel appraised?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I tried, but the expert was bitten by the turtle during the appraisal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, the turtle's supposed to shed its skin at some point between May and November,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:17.85,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,and I intended to wait until the turtle shed its skin so that I could take the jewel to the expert for an appraisal before I bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But I just couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:27.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I get it. He wanted to have a showdown with Kid while the jewel was still on the turtle's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Visitors' time is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Everybody apart from those involved with the case, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Stop faffing around and just get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's Inspector Nakamori, from Division 2 of the Police HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Division 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He's the inspector responsible for Kaitō Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah. When Kid-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s involved, he's always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:12:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So he's the one who's always being shown up by Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, son! Didn't you hear what I said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Everybody apart from those involved are to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ah, wait a second, Inspector Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sera-{\i1}san{\i0}'s from our high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And what do you mean 'son'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}After all, it's the first time I've met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's why you pulled my cheek, right? To see if I was Kid in disguise or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:28.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Right in the balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's Jeet Kune Do for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Since you're sweating like this, I guess you're not wearing a disguise either, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yo, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Dad! I thought you weren't coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I changed my mind when watching all of this on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And anyway, I was a bit worried about you for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}For once?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And another useless idiot shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:59.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After all that effort shutting out the visitors, why do we have to show a bunch of amateurs around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're to watch quietly from the back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well then, since we have 30 minutes left until\N 8 PM when he shows up, I'm going to the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The nearest toilet's crowded!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, when did {\i1}you{\i0} go to the toilet, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When we were touring the museum earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(0,250)}Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Comment: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The cheering for Kid's getting pretty loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}How long until Kid-{\i1}sama{\i0} appears?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Still, it's quite a guard you have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yes. This time, we're ready for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}In addition to the twenty men around the aquarium,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}we've got a hundred armed men with searchlights waiting in the passageway on the second floor with shining eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And the lights have batteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There's no way they'll go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Therefore, Kid won't be able to use the cover of darkness in his plan to steal the jewel this time, as he usually does!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:47.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He covered the tank with the carpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is he planning to steal the entire tank along with the carpet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sonoko, Sera-{\i1}san{\i0}, you two okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Never mind that, what about the jewel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You're joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I can't see it anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But there's a card in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}'The shy little mermaid has dissolved into foam and disappeared into my hands.'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}'Kaitō Kid.'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}T-The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:26.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:30.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How'd he pull it off in a situation like {\i1}this{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:40.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}T-The jewel disappeared along with the turtle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}T-That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Look for it! It's gotta be here in the tank somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Maybe in the shadow of a rock, or in the gravel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Kaitō Kid's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}'I have taken the jewel.'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}'If you don't believe me, check!'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Remove the locks on the aquarium mesh and bring me a step-ladder this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'll check the tank myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}How is it, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Is the turtle there or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I-It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}T-That's insane...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You can't come inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6}'Kaitō Kid got the treasure!'
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Damn it. Why are they cheering on the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, there isn't much we can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The tank was made from reinforced glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The sides and ceiling of the tank were covered in a steel mesh made from a special alloy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And while our eyes were covered by the carpet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}the deluxe turtle with the jewel on its back was stolen in a pretty spectacular way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}How do you know the tank's specs so well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hmph, it was on the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But wasn't this a little {\i1}too{\i0} well done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He'd planted all the strings in the carpet and set a winch under the chandelier to pull them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Didn't you check them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:18:00.31,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,{\blur1}Y-Yes, sir, but we'd heard that the carpet and the light {\blur1}had both been changed a few days before the tank was to be exhibited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What?! A few days before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We redid the carpet because a few days ago, a visitor sprayed cola around everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And the workers from the interior design company suggested we change the light to match the colour of the carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It seemed like a good opportunity for some redecorating,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}since we'd just moved all the artifacts from this room into another to make room for the tank, so I took up their offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But now that I think about it, those two workers could've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What do you mean, 'could have been'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Those {\i1}were{\i0} Kid and his accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}They already knew that the exhibition was gonna take place here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, I'm not going to stew over what's come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I've lost this time. Let's withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He's probably run far away from here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Or maybe that's what he made it look like, while he's still here in the gallery!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Because Kaitō Kid always disappears into the darkness or under a smokescreen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But this time, the light's been on the whole time, and he didn't even show himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If Kid {\i1}did{\i0} manage to steal the jewel with the turtle, then he should still be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And the guards blocking the entrance aren't making any moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}so I'd like to pinch the face of everybody in here like this and find out if Kid really {\i1}is{\i0} disguising himself as one of us or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But I feel bad about pinching the girls' faces, so how about we split off into groups and do some body searches?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Body searches?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Kid should still have the turtle with the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Isn't that right, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Y-Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Is that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}For me to be in the same group as you for the body search?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's fine. We'll check you all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So who do we start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}How about we go by ages and start with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}By ages? What month were you born in, Sera-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}More to the point, how do you even know our ages?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, Sera-{\i1}san{\i0}'s a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:32.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She really {\i1}is{\i0} flat as a board.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That spot feels nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Just shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:44.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was an impregnable tank, with its four sides made of reinforced glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:53.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the top and two sides covered with a special alloy mesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:58.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How did he get it out in that fraction of time in which our vision was obscured by the carpet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Put your hearts into the search! Kid's card was in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He might be hiding somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:12.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No. The trick with the card was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:16.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You roll up the card and tie it up with a string that dissolves in the water,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:21.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}then pass a fishing line through the card and put a small stone at the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:27.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If you hang that from the light and set it to fall from a remote controlled signal,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:36.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the card would fall and drop through the steel mesh, the thread would dissolve, and the message would be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:43.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Either way, the ones who got closest to the tank were Sera, Sonoko, the old man and Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:48.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They got bundled up in the carpet along with the guards who were already standing in front of the tank,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:51.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}so any of them could've put the card directly in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:55.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But the most suspicious person at the time was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:08.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey! Take your clothes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What about you over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:41.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We've finished the checks here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}S-Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.80,0:23:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Are you okay, Sonoko-{\i1}neechan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.29,0:23:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Everybody here was just being so weak-minded that it went to my head and I got really dizzy.{this is probably wrong}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.63,0:23:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There's only one person here who could slip past without a body check, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.13,0:23:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}...and you, Kaitō Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.80,0:24:04.80,Signs,,0,0,0,,(PART II)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.80,0:24:04.80,Signs,,0,0,0,,KAITŌ KID AND THE BLUSH MERMAID
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.80,0:24:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}On the next Conan: 'Kaitō Kid and the Blush Mermaid (Part II)'!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.80,0:24:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Next Conan's Hint: Magnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}I was barely {\i1}in{\i0} the episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.52,0:24:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}You were there all along in disguise, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}You never know!
